s:10:"1417818627";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14178186610";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158147;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158147";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:319:"/me happens to see Jay joining up with her group as they&#039;re preparing to depart from Bastion. She looks quite happy the showmare is coming along. &quot;Hey there! Haven&#039;t seen you since the last time I was in Bastion... what a trip that was!&quot; She giggled excitedly, hurrying over to give the mare a hug. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418860055";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188601130";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158163;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158163";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:206:"Jay looks quite visibly tired, although content. Half-awake and just going through the motions, Jay smiles and leans into the hug a little. &quot;O-oh, heeey~ I totally forget your name. Also my name.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418860267";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188602751";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158166;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158166";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:231:"&quot;Silly! You&#039;re not supposed to party before we make camp!&quot; She booped Jay&#039;s nose. &quot;I&#039;m Jay, and you&#039;re Crystal!&quot; She decided to see if the mare would catch that, because it was funny to her. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418860334";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188603919";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158183;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158183";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:127:"&quot;Aww... sorry. Hey Jay.&quot; She smiles broader, not registering the boop and just kinda leaning against &#039;Jay&#039;.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418860417";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188604249";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158186;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158186";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:77:"Pepper exists also, and is likely at Crystal&#039;s feet, headbutting gently.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418860441";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188604488";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158209;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158209";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:216:"/me giggles again. &quot;Wow you really are out of it.&quot; She released Jay so she could scoop up Pepper and snuggle the dog. &quot;Let&#039;s get you in bed. And not in the fun way. Just in the sleeping way.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418860725";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188607828";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158212;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158212";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:8:"to bed* ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418860771";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188608294";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158226;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158226";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:224:"Pepper fidgets some in Crystal&#039;s arms, but not a lot. Real-Jay is nearby so it&#039;s okay.[br][br]&quot;Out? I&#039;m here though...&quot; She mumbles, following Crystal. &quot;Bed would be cooool, I had a thing.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418860926";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188609338";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158258;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158258";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:502:"/me scritches the dog&#039;s head a bit before setting her down, gently, on the ground. Jay was cute, but this level of incoherence was hard for Crystal to see past. Cortege training meant never partying so hard that you would be useless if baddies came out of the shadows. Still, it happened to everyone sometimes. &quot;Alright then...&quot; She turned and used her talons to amplify her voice to call to the others. &quot;Hey! Bed! C&#039;mere!&quot; This would probably be a confusing thing to say.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418861151";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188612049";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158315;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158315";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:240:"Jay stays close to Crystal, moving slowly but confidently along, using the cart attached to her in order to keep herself steady. She has no idea what&#039;s going on.[br][br]Pepper stays close to Jay, protective but also still pretty happy.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418861772";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188617800";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158349;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158349";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:450:"/me keeps a wing draped over Jay. Her wings are notably larger than her Equestrian counterpart, and are actually proportionate to her body. Before long a rather large, strong looking buffalo approaches the two. He was carrying what looked to be the heaviest load of the cortege. Mainly formidable looking boxes covered in sheets. On the very top of the pile was a mattress and pillow. &quot;Hey! Jay, this is Al Bhed.&quot; The big buffalo just nods.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418862705";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188627628";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158351;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158351";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:170:"Jay stares at him in mild amazement. &quot;Is he gonna put that down?&quot; She asks, looking lazily toward Crystal. &quot;Or do I have to try and climb up there...&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418862972";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188629798";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158353;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158353";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"706";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:3:"Jay";s:4:"text";s:282:"/me giggles. &quot;Nope!&quot; She promptly scoops Pepper up and places her on the back of her neck where fur and feather meet, then, a moment later, scoops Jay up, sweeping her off her hooves. &quot;Up you go!&quot; She spread her wings and gave a strong flap to leave the ground. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418863225";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fa1818";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188632829";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158355;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158355";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:3:"Jay";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"880";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:19:"CrystalScratchovich";s:4:"text";s:431:"Both Jay and Pepper react the same; fidgeting a little but not a lot, just kinda going through the motions as necessary in a calm, content way.[br]Both Jay and Pepper would then curl in against each other adorably. Pepper could sleep if Jay wants to. A simple mind is equally capable of just sitting around for a while.[br]Jay is clearly in no state for coherent conversation, and it&#039;s probably not the result of JUST alcohol.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1418863462";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#16782c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14188634704";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#428bc9";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1158362;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1158362";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:19:"